Each user can only participate once, if repeated participation will lose the eligibility for prizes;

game rules

1: Answer the questions during the live broadcast time to participate in the award, and the fans who experience the first experience will win gifts;
2: Each user can only participate once;
3: You will get a value-for-money gift, it may be a Bluetooth headset, a lemon juice cup or juicer used in the kitchen, and of course an air fryer! ! Depends on MIUI.
4: The customer service has no right to modify the gift. All orders are automatically generated and shipped in the warehouse.
5: MIUI bears the international postage from China to the country/region where the customer is located, but if the postage does not meet the mailing conditions, you may need to pay part of the postage in your area. Please pay attention to this when shopping.
